title: r/arcbrowser
description: r/ArcBrowser is a forum to discuss Arc — a better way to use the internet. Arc is available on Mac and iOS, with plans to launch on Windows this year. Arc receives updates every Thursday. Note: r/ArcBrowser is not affiliated with The Browser Company.
